            text to be used as tooltip for the arrow button which pops up the menu. See
            <methodname><link linkend="method-gtktoolitem--set-tooltip">gtk.ToolItem.set_tooltip</link></methodname>()
            for setting a tooltip on the whole
            <link linkend="class-gtkmenutoolbutton"><classname>gtk.MenuToolButton</classname></link>.
        </para>
    </refsect2>

